descriptionHtml:
Magic Wand x SHOWFIELDS
SHOWFIELDS offers a genre-defying experience that’s part-retail store, and part-art exhibition. The store is also home to a revolving array of art, food, drink and community programming, aimed to facilitate deeper offline connections between brands and consumers.

Unlock exclusive content as you discover SHOWFIELDS, The Most Interesting Store in the World. Transform your device into a Magic Wand & enhance your in-store experience.

Use the Magic Wand to guide your discovery of more than 60 brands and artists currently at SHOWFIELDS. Engage with "magic" NFC tags throughout the store, simply by tapping your phone against the Magic Wand icons.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Completely new layout, possibility to scan products from stationary shop and POS Shopify integration to finalise order.
- the main functionality of the application is scanning QR codes of products from our stationary stores
- to scan the code, click scan on the floating menu
- to create a code for testing purposes,
* go to https://qr.io/
* select the text option
* enter the code: 180117
* scan the QR code created.
* add the product to your cart
* do checkout
